videos.headline: Troy takes punt return to the house
videos.description: Troy takes Nebraska's punt 58 yards to the end zone against the scoreless Cornhuskers.

videos.headline: Troy runs in 2nd TD
videos.description: B.J. Smith high-steps into the end zone after breaking away for a 9-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Bunch connects with Morgan Jr. for Nebraska TD
videos.description: Andrew Bunch connects with Stanley Morgan Jr. in the end zone for Nebraska's first touchdown against Troy.

videos.headline: Spielman hauls it in for Cornhuskers
videos.description: Andrew Bunch connects with JD Spielman on a 7-yard pass for a Cornhuskers score.
